  "Radik Shaimiev is co-owner of the TAIF Group, a large regional holding company with assets in the Republic of Tatarstan.",
  "TAIF became a shareholder in most of its companies during Russia's privatization in the mid '90s.",
  "Radik's father, Mintimer Shaimiev, was Tatarstan's first president and his brother, Airat Shaimiev, is a fellow billionaire."
